####### How to setup and run the Project ########
1.Download React Poeject Source code
https://github.com/Sahil989999/live-ecom-project/archive/refs/heads/main.zip 

2. Download  APi source Code
https://github.com/Sahil989999/live-ecom-project/archive/refs/heads/main.zip 

Note Setup the project
1.Download Source code from above url
2. unzip/extract the files from the folder
3. install nodejs 18+ version in your system
4. install react development environment using below code
npm install -g create-react-app
5.  install JSON-SERVER to run api
npm install -g json-sever
6.start the json-server using below command
    a. open cmd in api folder (that u have extrcted) and run.
json-server --watch db.json --port 1234

7. start react development server
    a. opeb cmd in react project folder that is "project 1" and run this command
npm start

    Note: You can you s Local host 3000

